Package: realestatebr
Type: Package
Title: Import Brazilian Real Estate Data into R
Version: 0.6.0
Authors@R: person(
    "Vinicius Oike", "Reginatto",
    email = "viniciusoike@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4425-9994")
    )
Description: Provides functions to import Brazilian real estate market data
    from various sources including BCB, FGV, ABECIP, ABRAINC, SECOVI, and BIS.
    Data is returned in tidy format for easy analysis and visualization.
